org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.pojo

Class TemporalElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.common.model.impl.pojo.EPGMElement
      • org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.pojo.TemporalElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Attributed, Element, Identifiable, Labeled
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TemporalGraphElement, TemporalGraphHead

    public abstract class TemporalElement
extends EPGMElement
implements Element
    Base class for all temporal elements. Contains interval definitions for transaction time and valid time.
